Package: cutpointr
Type: Package
Title: Methods for determining and evaluating optimal cutpoints in binary
    classification tasks
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Author: Christian Thiele
Maintainer: Christian Thiele <c.thiele@hs-osnabrueck.de>
Description: Apart from just picking the cutpoint that maximizes a chosen metric
    the package includes functions for bootstrapping and validating cutpoints.
